  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2301, Medium Earth Orbit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21-year-old Laurie's hikikomori life in her one-person space pod was peaceful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinkering with her bionic arms day in and day out was all she could ever ask for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But now that's all over...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aliens have launched an all-out attack on Earth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laurie's pod is shot down and collides with \"Colony 102\", rumored to harbor a secret weapon that can destroy the aliens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now the fate of humanity rests in her cold, metal hands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Metroidvania action:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the colony and unlock new skills and equipment, eventually gaining the ability to traverse the cold vacuum of space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a Metroidvania on a whole 'nother scale!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face off against huge bosses:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight bosses that take up nearly the entire screen as they unleash merciless attacks against Laurie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take 'em down and get that sense of accomplishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft your own equipment:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeated enemies will drop materials. Use them to craft new equipment and combine them with your skills to create a unique combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Into outer space:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have your vehicle, you can leave the colony and explore outer space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new combat style awaits, free from the shackles of gravity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vast expanse of space holds treasures for those willing to find them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vehicle can also be used inside the colony. Show your enemies no mercy!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2301, Medium Earth Orbit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21-year-old Laurie's hikikomori life in her one-person space pod was peaceful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinkering with her bionic arms day in and day out was all she could ever ask for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But now that's all over...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aliens have launched an all-out attack on Earth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laurie's pod is shot down and collides with \"Colony 102\", rumored to harbor a secret weapon that can destroy the aliens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now the fate of humanity rests in her cold, metal hands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Metroidvania action:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the colony and unlock new skills and equipment, eventually gaining the ability to traverse the cold vacuum of space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a Metroidvania on a whole 'nother scale!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face off against huge bosses:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight bosses that take up nearly the entire screen as they unleash merciless attacks against Laurie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take 'em down and get that sense of accomplishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft your own equipment:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeated enemies will drop materials. Use them to craft new equipment and combine them with your skills to create a unique combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Into outer space:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have your vehicle, you can leave the colony and explore outer space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new combat style awaits, free from the shackles of gravity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vast expanse of space holds treasures for those willing to find them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vehicle can also be used inside the colony. Show your enemies no mercy!</p>",
